  "title": "Clinical Nutrition & F&B Coordinator",
  "description": "<h3>💼 Job Description</h3><p>We are seeking motivated and service-oriented individuals to join our Food & Beverage team in a reputable healthcare environment. Successful candidates will support daily meal services for in-patients and hospital events, ensuring high standards of service and patient satisfaction.<br /><br /><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Salary range $1800 - $2700</p></li><li><p>Working days: 5 days</p></li><li><p>Working Location: Novena, Central</p></li><li><p>Benefits: AWS + 2-3months Performance Bonus + Career Stability + Annual Salary increment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Coordinate and ensure smooth operations of F&B services for in-patient meals and internal events</p></li><li><p>Take and compile meal orders for private and special diet patients</p></li><li><p>Ensure food trolleys are properly heated before meal dishing</p></li><li><p>Dispatch meals to wards accurately and on time</p></li><li><p>Attend to and resolve patient enquiries or complaints professionally</p></li><li><p>Compile patient feedback and reports for management review</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum Secondary education</p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills (MS Word, Outlook, Excel)</p></li><li><p>Able to work in a healthcare environment and in a team</p></li></ul><p>Applicants who possess relevant experience for the above responsibilities are most welcome to apply. If you do not possess the above experience, your application will still be considered on individual merits and you may be contacted for other opportunities.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</a></p><p><strong>Yong Jia Wen</strong></p><p><strong>Registration Number: R25146805</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 13C6730 (MCI Consulting Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
